{"id":254346,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-安徽黄克锦赴京谈生意被维稳截访（/","date":"2012-09-30T02:46:13Z","modified":"2012-09-30T02:46:13Z","title":"维权网 | 安徽黄克锦赴京谈生意被维稳“截访”（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员周维林报道）安徽省合肥市肥东县黄克锦向本网信息员反映，其因土地、房屋补偿诉求已经于今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月与合肥循环经济示范园达成协议解决，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日夜黄克锦欲乘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">K1110</span><span>次列车赴京，赴京目的是与北京一商家洽谈加工圆珠笔业务，孰料，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>分，在合肥火车站第二候车室，来了四男一女对其采取暴力拦截，当时黄克锦要求他们出示证件，无人理会，打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警电话三次，这些人称“你打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>也没有用。”而且还要搜他的包，火车站工作人员上前询问，其中一人对其耳语后就不管不顾。夜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>时许黄克锦被他们带回肥东县店埠镇家中，他知道这四男一女是肥东县店埠镇的截访人员，其中女子是肥东县信访局工作人员。第二天黄克锦到中共安徽省纪委投诉此事，省纪委则转合肥市纪委办理；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>又向安徽省公安厅投诉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日下午</span><span>肥东县检察院检察长接待，控申科科长竟然将其投诉材料撕毁……目前，黄克锦就</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>被非法拦截一事多方投诉无门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黄克锦与妻子因土地及房屋补偿问题上访，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>在合肥火车站欲乘车赴京上访被肥东县截访人员非法拦截，黄克锦妻子因此住院治疗，此后又为此而上访投诉，本网曾于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>分别予以报道。如今，黄克锦因诉求已经于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月获得解决不再上访，并积极地寻找商机，欲在市场经济中圆其发家致富之梦，可是维稳人员就是因为其曾经是访民而采取非法暴力拦截，置其权利于不顾，令其不仅商机丧失，身心受到伤害，故再次走上上访之路，要求法律制裁对其采取非法暴力拦截的四男一女的刑事责任或行政责任。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>安徽访民黄克锦夫妇上访被限制人身自由</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/03/blog-post_6515.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/03/blog-post_6515.html</a></span></div>\n<div><span>合肥访民黄克锦夫妇就被非法拘禁等提出控告</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/04/blog-post_3691.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2011/04/blog-post_3691.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iYluKODiqqE/UGer_V2f-gI/AAAAAAAAP-U/sAGTZClM5Yo/s1600/P1030135.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-iYluKODiqqE/UGer_V2f-gI/AAAAAAAAP-U/sAGTZClM5Yo/s320/P1030135.JPG\" width=\"225\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SpYBuEjNUw8/UGesBV_aW-I/AAAAAAAAP-c/iRdfFZAdcgc/s1600/P1030139.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SpYBuEjNUw8/UGesBV_aW-I/AAAAAAAAP-c/iRdfFZAdcgc/s320/P1030139.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-mMyJs1tXkvA/UGesC-qPp8I/AAAAAAAAP-k/k5_1s3qw2aE/s1600/P1030140.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-mMyJs1tXkvA/UGesC-qPp8I/AAAAAAAAP-k/k5_1s3qw2aE/s320/P1030140.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7853590622492297663?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST